dct_title_s: The gold and coal fields of Alaska : together with the principal steamer routes and trails
dct_description_sm: Relief shown in hachures. Includes parts of the Yukon Territory and northern British Columbia. Includes 2 inset maps: The Klondike gold region, Canada -- Trails from Tide Water to the headwaters of the Yukon River, Alaska. Accompanied by: Map of Alaska : showing known gold-bearing rocks ... Washington, D.C. : United States Geological Survey, 1898. 44 p. Historic Maps copy lacks accompanying text.
